- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of speech recognition in healthcare communication skills teaching. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper involves videoconferencing interactions. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms in automatic speech recognition systems.
